The blade slashes Dinotron's hip. He roars in pain, but he could endure the 
pain for a while. He takes a step back, limping on his wounded leg. 

"Your going to pay for that!" He yells.

He then gets an idea. 

He smiles mischieviously at Aerotaur.

Then he fires off 3 shots from his optics.
